text: I've fallen out of the habit of Google reviews but this place, without any incentivisation from them at all to do this, makes me want to give them 5 stars. Superb service, with amazing collections - Loved their Peach Momoko catalog and the owner was really friendly and encouraging, with great prices to boot. Would have gone and bought more, if it weren't for my budget (which I exceeded anyway), but this just means more trips there in the future and I don't mind that at all! Excited for future visits

I've been a regular at Inkink Collectibles for some time now, and it never disappoints! The owner is incredibly friendly and always makes you feel welcome. The shop has an amazing variety of comics, ranging from classic titles to the latest releases, as well as a fantastic selection of collectibles. Whether you're a comic enthusiast or looking for something unique, this is the place to go. Highly recommended for both casual readers and hardcore collectors!
HJ was so awesome! I loved the art and meeting the artist!
